title: ARCTIC Alpine 64 GT Rev. 2 CPU Cooler - AMD, Supports Multiple Sockets, 80mm PWM Fan at 22dBA
description: ARCTIC Alpine 64 GT Rev. 2 is a cost-effective fan/heatsink combo AMD CPU cooler featuring a 80mm ultra-quiet PWM-controlled fan, all-aluminum construction heatsinks and non-capacitive, non-electricity-conductive MX-2 thermal compound. The efficient design provides 70W of peak cooling power yet at less than 23dBA of fan noise. Simple mounting mechanism making ARCTIC Alpine 64 GT Rev. 2 extremely easy to install compare to similar CPU coolers. Fluid dynamic bearing extends the operating lifespan of the fan while ensures quiet operation.  ARCTIC Alpine 64 GT Rev. 2 comes with a 6-year limited peace-of-mind warranty and is an ideal replacement/upgrade to AMD stock CPU cooler, supporting AMD Socket FM2+/FM2/AM3+/AM3/AM2+/AM2/939/754.
